

# MERN Trello Backend

A backend service built with **MERN stack** (MongoDB, Express.js, Node.js) for managing teams and a task board with columns: **TODO → DOING → DONE**. This project includes authentication, team management, task management, activity logging, caching, rate limiting, and API documentation.

