## Installation & Running Locally

1. Clone the repository:
   
   git clone https://github.com/amandadhwal/Treello_Backend_Services.git
   cd backend
 
2. Install dependencies:

   npm install
 
3. Copy `.env.example` to `.env` and update values.
4. Start MongoDB

5. Start the server:

   npm run dev
   




