## Features

* **User Authentication**: Register, login with JWT, hashed passwords, protected routes.
* **Team Management**: Create teams, add/remove members, view members (creator-only restrictions).
* **Task Board**: Create, update, delete tasks; move between columns; assign tasks; comment on tasks.
* **Caching**: Redis caching for team task lists with invalidation on updates.
* **Rate Limiting**: Protect login and activity endpoints.
* **Error Handling**: Meaningful HTTP status codes and messages.
* **API Documentation**: Swagger/OpenAPI or Postman collection.

## API Endpoints (Overview)

* **Auth**

  * `POST /api/auth/register` — Register new user
  * `POST /api/auth/login` — Login
* **Teams**

  * `POST /api/teams` — Create team
  * `POST /api/teams/:teamId/members` — Add member (creator only)
  * `DELETE /api/teams/:teamId/members` — Remove member (creator only)
  * `GET /api/teams/:teamId/members` — List members
* **Tasks**

  * `POST /api/teams/:teamId/tasks` — Create task
  * `GET /api/teams/:teamId/tasks` — List tasks (cached, pagination, search, filter)
  * `PUT /api/teams/:teamId/tasks/:taskId` — Update task
  * `DELETE /api/teams/:teamId/tasks/:taskId` — Delete task
  * `POST /api/teams/:teamId/tasks/:taskId/move` — Move task
  * `POST /api/teams/:teamId/tasks/:taskId/assign` — Assign task
  * `POST /api/teams/:teamId/tasks/:taskId/comments` — Comment on task
* **Activity**

  * `GET /api/teams/:teamId/activities` — Get activities (rate limited)

